articles.author: Yashaswini
articles.title: Surging dengue virus in Bengaluru poses threat to women, kids: Doctors
articles.description: With dengue spreading its tentacles once again, hospitals are seeing a significant rise in incidence of the vector-borne disease among women and child.
articles.content: Unforgettable train journeys across Indias best landscape

articles.author: TNN
articles.title: BBMP audit confirms 1 dengue death, 213 new cases in Bengaluru
articles.description: In Kaggadasapura, a 27-year-old man succumbed to dengue amid a surge of 1,742 cases in June. Pregnant women and children face high risks. Hospitals like SPARSH and Motherhood handle daily dengue cases, emphasizing preventive measures for all.
articles.content: Unforgettable train journeys across Indias best landscape

articles.author: CBS News
articles.title: Advocates use end of Pride Month to warn about Mpox
articles.description: Celebrations across the country are marking the end of Pride Month. Advocates are using the opportunity to warn about Mpox in the hopes of avoiding a breakout similar to the one in 2022. Dr. Celine Gounder reports.
